high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen sink behind you.
Pick up the blue plate off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the oven and look up at the microwave.

Open the microwave and put the blue plate inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave back up and take the now heated plate out, then close the microwave.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the section of counter to the left of the stove.
Put the heated blue plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated blue plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right, go forward to the left side of the sink.
Take the blue plate from the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the oven, go to the oven.
Heat the plate in the microwave above the oven. Take the plate from the oven.
Go to the counter to the left of the oven.
Put the plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot plate on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Pick up the blue plate on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn left and walk to the stove and microwave.
Heat up the plate in the microwave.
Place the plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate on a counter.
